# MorphoWrite

## Setup

python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate

pip install -r requirements.txt

## Run locally

make dev

make stop

App:
http://localhost:8080

Add a .env file in project root specifying YOUR:
SECRET_KEY=
DEBUG=True
GEMINI_API_KEY=
DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE=config.settings.local 
ALLOWED_HOSTS=127.0.0.1,localhost,


## Static files
Uses Tailwind CDN for development, no config.